3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing high resolution satellite images. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes an improved anomaly-based model for ship detection. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly deal with distributed or parallel computing, but it may involve some computational aspects related to processing large satellite images.
